VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (api[_-]?key|secret|token|password)\s*[:=]\s*"[^"]{8,}"
WHEN EXPR MISSING:example|sample|dummy|test|placeholder|TODO|\$\{
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects likely hardcoded secret material in Android code/config.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for Android Hardcoded Secret Marker.
